description:
This is a 18 minute workout called '15 MIN EXPRESS PILATES WORKOUT || Dynamic Intermediate Pilates (No Equipment)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.
